partnerDetails.about: Get switched onto the power of Transform Electrical. Transform Electrical is the Eastern Cape's leader in the Electrical Wholesale industry, with branches in Port Elizabeth, East London, King Williams Town, George, Plettenberg Bay and Cape Town. Transform has showrooms throughout the Eastern Cape, for all your domestic and industrial lighting requirements
